# Fuzzer-discovered edge cases

=== trailing backslash escape
echo $?\
---
(command (word "echo") (word "$?\\\\"))
---


=== space between redirect operator and ampersand
< &-
---
<error>
---

=== semicolon in parameter length expansion
${#a;b}
---
(command (word "${#a;b}"))
---

=== newline in array assignment with trailing text
a=(
)b
---
(command (word "a=()b"))
---

=== trailing backslash at EOF in heredoc
a <<X
\
---
(command (word "a") (redirect "<<" "\\"))
---
=== backslash-escaped dollar in quoted command substitution
"\\$(a)$(b)"
---
(command (word "\"\\\\$(a)$(b)\""))
---
=== brace-close before redirect operator
{]}>a
---
(command (word "{]}") (redirect ">" "a"))
---

=== space after bang in parameter expansion
${! a}
---
(command (word "${! a}"))
---
